hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bd953a6266e6424460b94e5bff3bbba78cc6b6","tid":2119651,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"嘴炮到此為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ace70b257ff8db9d39b075316acad60b067138","tid":2119651,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"遲d腥港乜柒外國領事館都關哂就真係疊埋心水共享祖國榮耀喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cc1519710c334fc3c135d263b436ef7e3b078b","tid":2119651,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"開戰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打，奉陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a72f29336884fbb03b95ed2c807f6980092266","tid":2119651,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"支那如果唔求其選一間美國駐支領事館關閉，我睇面子好難落台<br />\n<br />\n不如就選香港啦，香港美領假假地都直屬國務院，要玩就玩大d"},{"pid":"eddf231191e106b764c314274620744d8ca7a4e5","tid":2119651,"uid":34666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"476191e37f15162bd3ff4da606d9ce10b268ceb9","tid":2119651,"uid":84044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"374663b738e03ea11a27053e2af274e4bf90f774","tid":2119651,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2700000/2702848/20200722_houston_v1_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2700000%2F2702848%2F20200722_houston_v1_600.png&h=de54aeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美角力持續升溫，中國官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進指出，美國要求中方在72小時內關閉駐休斯敦總領事館，是「喪心病狂」。外交部證實美方突然要求關閉使館，並敦促美方立即撤銷決定，否則中方必將作出正當和必要反應。<br />\n<